{"tid":753832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離岸人民幣急跌　曾失守6.84關口  再創逾一年低","createTime":"2018-07-24T02:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T04:26:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d39720333770d135cdda4947668ce6a8870424aa","tid":753832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1408548_1_L_20180724095959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1408548_1_L_20180724095959.jpg&h=b57b5308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408548-20180724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408548-20180724.htm&d=yNkmeMlVCs07GOpqs1huSzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3b425cfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408548-20180724.htm&h=4917356a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408548-20180724.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n人民幣持續尋底，離岸人民幣一度急跌超過400點子，失守6.84關口，其後跌幅收窄，較早時在6.839水平上落，跌逾350點子。<br />\n<br />\n在岸人民幣跌穿6.82，低見6.8246，較昨日夜市收市跌超過250點子。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣貶值，一方面與隔晚美元上升有，另一方面，昨日國務院常務會議確定積極財政政策「要更加積極」與金融政策「協同發力」，申萬宏源指，市場形成了對政策邊際放鬆的一致預期。"},{"pid":"0c362c885fd4a510bda967f6435f2cdfd9bceb11","tid":753832,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"之前玩冥幣定期既婆仔<br />\n<br />\n賺息蝕匯水, 倒蝕鳥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9444c6d6d833e38ec713090e451b61588e8538fb","tid":753832,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"股市大升"},{"pid":"dfb86cc55c4db4bf990c744f0f5ac7fbc321ce39","tid":753832,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"034e7bad701959c90c205c2f45566f4ba9b6187b","tid":753832,"uid":193555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7aa1b0ec85f67237ad50eef790d76d13d513621","tid":753832,"uid":77614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbb80c29b341d1e87970792d5c5fd84e582576bf","tid":753832,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"人幣即期開市大跌３１１點子，再次跌穿６﹒８<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社２４日專訊》人民幣兌一美元中間價今報６﹒７８９１，續創去年７月以來<br />\n最低，較上個交易日貶２９８點子。<br />\n　　人民幣兌一美元即期匯率（ＣＮＹ）今早低開３１１點子，報６﹒８１４５，再次跌穿<br />\n６﹒８關口，上個交易日即期匯率收盤報６﹒７８３４。<br />\n　　離岸人民幣延續昨（２３日）晚跌勢，今早一度跌穿６﹒８４，低見６﹒８４４８，急瀉<br />\n４０８點子，目前在６﹒８３水平徘徊。<br />\n　　國務院常務會議確定財政政策要更加積極，與金融政策協同發力，更好應對外部環境不確定<br />\n性，而隔晚美匯指數回升，均推低人民幣匯率。（ｋｌ）"},{"pid":"05f5879f570a26e45ee0411b8cb385ceb132cf65","tid":753832,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">穿埋6.95先至戲肉呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b7b3f1a769abf6359fe2a48fef467a6236462791","tid":753832,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"變廢紙未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073185a18f589aeab972b8d26e6bd8229b5e23c4","tid":753832,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75b778fc5a3230ad5b818f6a2697d2d1076802fc","tid":753832,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"034e7bad701959c90c205c2f45566f4ba9b6187b","tid":753832,"uid":1